  "text": "While each product featured is independently selected by our editors, we may include paid promotion. If you buy something through our links, we may earn commission. Read more about our Product Review Guidelines here.Layering season is nearly upon us, which means it's almost time to break out our favorite coats, boots, and, of course, sweaters. If you're looking for a fresh variety of styles, Amazon carries a huge range, including chunky turtlenecks, fuzzy cardigans, polished sweater coats, and more. You can choose between oversize and cozy options that mimic the feel of your favorite throw blanket or dressier sweaters you can pair with a skirt or trousers.To get you set for fall, we curated a collection of stylish and highly-rated options from Amazon at affordable price points. Nearly every pick we found is under $50, with prices starting at $20. Aside from an amazing value, you won't have to wait long until your new sweater arrives at your doorstep. Ahead, shop our 15 favorite Amazon sweaters you'll reach for all season long.amazon.comBest Sleeveless SweaterSaodimallsu Women's Cap-Sleeve Top ($20) If you're looking for a sweater that you can wear as the weather slowly but surely transitions into fall, this one's a pretty brilliant option. It'll look great with jeans or trousers and won't leave you sweating when the afternoons heat up again.amazon.comBest Lightweight CardiganAmazon Essentials Women's Lightweight V-Neck Cardigan Sweater ($22, originally $23) We can always count on Amazon Essentials for our wardrobe staples, and cardigans are no exception. It comes in nearly every color imaginable and has thousands of rave reviews from shoppers who love its softness, lightweight feel, and flattering fit.amazon.comBest Striped SweaterETCYY Oversized Sweater ($30, originally $40) The crewneck and stripes on this sweater feel classic, while the oversized fit, dropped shoulders, and exposed seams add a hint of edge. It has over 1,000 reviews and a solid 4.4 rating, so it's a steal at this price.amazon.comBest Chunky Loose-Knit SweaterUgerlov Women's Oversized Sweater ($35) The loose, chunky weave of this sweater reminds us of a cozy throw blanket in the best way. It features batwing sleeves and a subtle mock neck.amazon.comBest Turtleneck SweaterAsvivid Turtleneck Sweater ($37) You'll feel comfortable and cozy in this turtleneck sweater. The fit will allow you to move freely, while the fabric is great for keeping chills away.amazon.comBest Cable-Knit SweaterANRABESS Women's Oversized Cable Knit Sweater ($37, originally $43) This cable-knit sweater is the perfect lookalike to the one Rory Gilmore famously wore in the first episode of \"Gilmore Girls,\" and it's been garnering lots of buzz among TikTokers who want to recreate the Y2K aesthetic. Amazon shoppers are loving it too. One five-star reviewer described it as the \"perfect Rory Gilmore sweater,\" adding that it \"gives the chunky look but isn't excessively thick.\"PS Photography | Marisa PetrarcaBest Oversize SweaterANRABESS Women's Crewneck Pullover Sweater ($40, originally $63) This sweater is an Amazon bestseller in women's pullover sweaters, and we understand the appeal. The incredibly soft fabric rivals popular luxury blankets, so you feel enveloped in comfort with plenty of room to move. Tuck the front into a pair of jeans or trousers to balance the volume. One of our editors put it to the test and confirmed it's worth the hype. Read her ANRABESS Women's Crewneck Pullover Sweater review for more. Editor Quote: \"What I love most about the Anrabess Oversized Fuzzy Knit Sweater is how soft it is. The look and feel remind me of my Barefoot Dreams Blanket, and I'm not alone in this. At the time of writing, 25 shoppers have compared it to one as well. The best part is that it doesn't make me feel overly hot throughout the day, likely thanks to its slightly oversize fit. I appreciate that it's thick and stitched tightly, ensuring it's not see-through, which makes it feel very high-quality. The large, folded cuffs are such a stylish addition as well.\" — Marisa Petrarca, contributing editor, ShoppingAmazonBest Batwing SweaterLillusory Crewneck Batwing Long Sleeve Sweater ($40, originally $60) While this batwing sweater has plenty of cozy volume, the vertical grain cuffs, side slits, and ribbed texture save it from looking frumpy. It's the perfect sweater to throw on over leggings, leather skinny pants, or straight-leg jeans. It also happens to be Amazon's topseller in the women's sweaters category, so it's a popular choice.amazon.comBest Sweater JacketAnrabess Open Front Sweater Jacket ($47, originally $70) Lighter and softer than a coat but more structured than your typical cardigan, this open-front cardigan jacket will get a ton of use. It comes in 24 colors, so you may be tempted to pick up more than one.- — Additional reporting by Marisa PetrarcaAngela Elias is a contributing editor for PS Shopping. In her former roles at PS, she led the relaunch of its Latine identity and family-focused verticals, directed its Home vertical, and hosted shopping segments on TV Guide Network and video content for brands like Pier 1 and Walgreens. She has nearly 15 years of experience working in the lifestyle space as a writer, editor, content strategist, director, on-camera talent, and publicist.Marisa Petrarca is a contributing editor for PS Shopping and has more than five years of experience writing and editing beauty, fashion, and lifestyle content. Her work has been featured in Cosmopolitan, Allure, and InStyle, among others.",
